# Handwritten Digit Recognition

AI-based handwritten digit recognition web application using Flask and TensorFlow.

## Features
- Draw digits (0–9)
- Predict handwritten numbers
- Deep learning model using MNIST dataset
- Interactive web interface

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Flask
- TensorFlow
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Run Locally

```bash
python app.py
```

Open:
http://127.0.0.1:5000
